>Description:
It would be nice if the Preferences dialog keyboard shortcut were Command-comma rather than Command-semicolon. Command-comma is the standard Preferences shortcut for Mac applications:

http://developer.apple.com/documentation/UserExperience/Conceptual/OSXHIGuidelines/XHIGWindows/chapter_17_section_6.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/20000961-TPXREF57
